00:01:17.870 --> 00:01:19.029
(It's aching)

00:01:19.029 --> 00:01:23.045
If I confess it, there's no going back

00:01:23.479 --> 00:01:26.012
and I'd regret it

00:01:26.012 --> 00:01:30.845
Before I knew it,
this aching and pain have crept up

00:01:31.012 --> 00:01:34.529
